}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The FCC ID printed on the label is probably XU8TEW646UBH. :The FCC ID of the OEM parent product is SCD030021. Device is a [[LanReady WUB1900H5|LanReady WUB1902H5]].
:Only one device is indicated in the driver file to be a TRENDnet device :(USB\VID_20F4&PID_646B/20f4:646b) and the description jives with the long :description of this device ("High Power 150Mbps Wireless N USB Adapter").. :this ID is thus assumed to be 20f4:646b.
